1. Kupio sam *robu* u prodavnici. (I bought *goods* in the store.)
2. On je nelegalno prodavao *robu*. (He was selling *contraband* illegally.)
3. *Roba* je stigla na luku. (The *cargo* has arrived at the port.)
4. Njihov biznis se bavi prodajom *robe* na veliko. (Their business deals with selling *merchandise* wholesale.)
5. Ne želim da budem *roba* sistema. (I don't want to be a *slave* of the system.)
6. Sud ga je proglasio *robnim* kreditom. (The court declared it as a *pledge* loan.)
7. Životinje su držane u nehumanim uslovima kao *roba*. (The animals were kept in inhumane conditions as *commodities*.)
8. Trenutno nije bilo raspoložive *robe* u prodavnici. (There was currently no available *stock* in the store.)
9. Ona se bavi trgovinom *robom* iz Azije. (She trades *goods* from Asia.)
10. *Roba* je bila oštećena tokom transporta. (The *merchandise* was damaged during transportation.)